overview: As of 3/13/2022 - WB Cancelled Wonder Woman 3  ************************************************************************************ The final sequel in the Wonder Woman trilogy from DC and Warner Bros.  Diana Prince (Gal Gadot) has always sworn to protect mankind - from chaos and destruction of its own making - as Wonder Woman for over a century. But in the present day, the more crimes she stops, the more people are on to her and bent on discovering her secrets. When a new threat rises, Diana must turn to unlikely allies and take on new enemies to save the world again - this time, from the mystical machinations of the wicked sorceress Circe (Tilda Swinton).
title: Wonder Woman 3
